dc_title_s: Map of the city of Detroit, Michigan, showing streets with house numbers, street car lines and location of principal industrial, educational and religious buildings; Drawn and published by Sauer bros. and Frydrych, 1912.
dc_description_s: Historical sketch compiled by C. M. Burton, city histrographer & data prepared by board of Commerce. Street index. 1 map: col.; 56 x 84 cm. This map is in the public domain. Please attribute access and use of this digitized map to the Stephen S. Clark Library, University of Michigan Library.
